603
01:02:50,333 --> 01:02:51,129
No ...

604
01:03:10,520 --> 01:03:12,112
Are you Dr. Jotaro Nagao?

605
01:03:13,055 --> 01:03:13,885
Yes.

606
01:03:17,026 --> 01:03:20,325
Sadako Yamamura ... You know her don't you?

607
