Hey you -

608
01:03:28,838 --> 01:03:30,499
what did you do to her?

609
01:03:35,912 --> 01:03:37,345
Sadako ...

610
01:03:49,759 --> 01:03:52,922
It was over 30 years ago.

611
01:03:54,330 --> 01:03:59,632
